QX|3.,wide|ht|b|CS|1|CP|4|fp|1|at|^-{      The Requirements      }
^-|CS||CP||fp||at|
^B@2As in any ace asking conventions the trump suit must be clearly established and both partners should be on the same page. Then, the suit used to initiate the call for Keycards, as is called Kickback suit, is the suit in rank above the agreed trump suit and the Kickback bid is four of the Kickback suit. When the trump suit is clearly established it is not important whether this suit has been previously bid by anyone on the table or not. Please indulge us with repeating some of information. |
PG| ***** 30 ***** |


ht|k|CS|1|CP|4|fp|1|at|^-{      When to Use the Kickback Convention       }
^-|CS||CP||fp||at|^B@2
Most expert partnerships use Kickback Keycard Ask for all four suits, Minor suits and Major suits. However, some partnerships use Kickback conventional method only when the trump is a Minor suit (Redwood Convention). |
