cp|8|AT|

^B@2^*BMarilyn Hemenway: ^*N|cp||at| First, there are some disadvantages of using Kickback. One is that the now RKC asking bid is no longer available as a cuebid. Likewise, you can't splinter in that suit. For example, in the next auction:|
