ht|i|va|4|cs|6|at|^B{|ia|,1sp3cp4cp!4d|at|}|HT|i|va|4|at|^m@24@D would normally be a cuebid, showing an Ace or Void or a singleton in Diamonds. However, playing Kickback it would be Keycard Ask for clubs. One solution to cuebidding is to play that 4NT is the equivalent of a cuebid in the Kickback suit.|
