HT|n|at|^B@2Kickback can cause you problems though. Attempting to use Kickback instead of 4NT as RKC is guaranteed to give you and your partner many headaches and at least 10 bad or below average boards until you BOTH begin to remember it and use it to your advantage. ^*BHowever, don't knock it until you've tried it.^*N|
